LINUX

Use the given Makefile, or a variant thereof.

WINDOWS

Preliminaries:

Make sure that you have glut installed (glut32.lib, glut32.dll, glut.h).
You can get these from:
   http://www.opengl.org/resources/libraries/glut/glutdlls37beta.zip

Microsoft Visual Studio C++ v6.0
Associated files:   a0.dsw  a0.dsp
You'll want to open a0.dsw .

Microsoft Visual Studio .Net C++ v7
Files:    a0.sln   a0.vcproj
You'll want to open a0.sln .



